Over half of my constituents rely on Medicaid, and many go to Olive View for healthcare.

@HouseGOP's Medicaid cuts will have a disastrous effect on communities across the country.

To pay for tax cuts for their billionaire donors, @HouseGOP's budget would cut Medicaid for over 370,000 people in CA-29.

This includes over 133,000 children and 45,000 seniors.

@HouseDemocrats are fighting back to protect Medicaid for working families across the country. https://t.co/2roDCLiOWL

